Types of API
-----------
Private API-to communicater internally inside application
public-communication-inbetween 2 or more application
eg:Linkedin/blazemeter-direct login (or)login using Google Account-logging in using another app credentials
1.google exposes API publically-so linkedin,blazemeter,nauki -indirect login

2.GoogleMAP,Rapido,OLA-Public APIs-so using in android&ios

Private API
-----------
Payments Gateway-only for Specific person to pay that payment
asks for authentication&Authorization(oatuh2)

