process:REQ,RES
------------
CLIENT IDE<->API<->SERVER API()

HTTP METHODS:

CLIENT IDE<-Req->API<-Res->SERVER API()

CRUD-Create Read Update Delete

types of methods:to interact with servers-API to test-need 5 basic API methods
1.Get-get the resource(safe-no modification only reading)
2.Post-Create new resource-posting payload-creating new resource
3.Put-Update Entire Resouce-add new column or row -new record into DB-adding new employee or adding new criteria for emplyee records
4.Patch-partial update-update one field value -changing salary from 50k to 1.5L
5.Delete-Delete entire record like -Deleting 1 Employee from DB table

