what is needed for API to Send Request
Request:
----------
1.Http method(get,post,patch,put0	
2.PAyload(data)
3.Header(payload additional details)
4.Endpoint(addr)
5.Authorization
Reponse:
----------
1.StatusCode
2.StatusMsg
3.Cookies
4.Headers

