BDD-IN POSTMAN-WE USE GHERKIN LANGUAGE  -LIKE CUCUMBER-FEATUREFILE(using given,when,then)

here in postman we use either plain gherkin language to validate --> pm.response.to.have.status(200);
				or
assertions using chai library- mocha chai library is a -assertion for JS language 
uses mostly 1.expect() or 2.Should()/should not			-->pm.expect(pm.response.status).is.equal(200);


